# Agent Test Run Reporting

When running `C-API` or `C-UI` tests:

- Save a per-run report in `allReports/` with agent, environment, timestamp, and full test output.
- Do not commit generated files inside `allReports/`; only `allReports/.gitkeep` is tracked.
- Push/deploy only when code or schema changed, or when the user explicitly asks.
